      <pubtit>Nanofabricated tips as a platform for double-tip and device based scanning tunneling microscopy</pubtit>
      <p><img src="/images/pubpic/SmartPub.png" class="img-responsive" width="33%" style="float: left" /></p>
      <p>We introduce a platform for bringing new, device-based functionality to STM, with the goal of utilizing decades of progress in device engineering for the field of scanning probe.</p>
      <p><em>M Leeuwenhoek,  RA Norte, KM Bastiaans, Doohee Cho, I Battisti, YaM Blanter, S GrÃ¶blacher, MP Allan</em></p>
